    "body": "You can use the [`searchFunction`](https://community.algolia.com/instantsearch.js/v2/instantsearch.html#struct-InstantSearchOptions-searchFunction). In there you can use the helper [methods](https://community.algolia.com/algoliasearch-helper-js/reference.html) to get the currently refined options and finally set `hitsPerPage` to the value needed before searching. \r\n\r\nFeel free to reopen if you need more information.",
